{"tid":562861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生哥望增高識女神","createTime":"2018-02-16T09:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T13:49:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a473cc1b3e0f895a5867a8810c59df9497eca16c","tid":562861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180216/20307163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F20307163&d=6R1NWmwuYKdQhY7l7wlf8b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=88faafe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F20307163&h=6df7eae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180216/20307163</a><br />\n<br />\n學生哥望增高識女神<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n狗年來臨，學生哥各有不同願望，小一的梁同學最實際，希望「成績好啲，可以買多啲玩具」；小二的袁同學則希望不要再遲交功課，有患濕疹同學仔希望來年濕疹受控，並在學校校慶表演跳繩時順利；小二的劉同學希望獲得1,000元大利是，可以購買iPhone和iPad，更渴望不用做家務。<br />\n<br />\n至於中一的鄭同學則希望可以增高，「最好有1.6米」；他的波友李同學（圖）除希望籃球技術提升，亦夢想結識一名長髮可愛女朋友；中二的何同學希望選修合適科目，並可獲派公屋「上樓」改善居住環境；他的同學王同學則希望可去海洋公園玩。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃麗兒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180216/large/16la5p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F16la5p11.jpg&h=21815d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t動記者去求籤　問香港狗年運程<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t或有高官下台　法治存暗湧<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t林鄭治港跟習主席？港人：依家嘅政府無希望<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t股市大上大落　樓價仍高企<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t攝太歲後需擇吉還神<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t哈日情侶想中六合彩<br />\n要聞 11小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t《蘋果》求籤　港運勢入秋有轉機一國兩制續受威脅　雙鄭民望恐插水<br />\n要聞 11小時前"},{"pid":"97ce9d10cfb243768f1b3cdb4503a91e509d2d7f","tid":562861,"uid":43042,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"應該唔關高度事"},{"pid":"44b1d9b230e58e2b09effee4fa84d26af70b33c2","tid":562861,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"王心凌新目標....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-05-2018/cjLDyV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-05-2018%2FcjLDyV.gif&h=514496be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2018-02-20(下周二、年初五)20:00\t- 傑志 vs 全北汽車(韓國)\t@香港大球場</span>"},{"pid":"a4c8a85007f3e7a78aaba17dc406099dd555775f","tid":562861,"uid":402,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"1.6米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2ecd2f4c958f6399c6bec739a69a1db2d563cd","tid":562861,"uid":71726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f27a9b9233eaeba4639bba0220af335e7d718a","tid":562861,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"佢老豆咩身家？"},{"pid":"b77615a09568586ac1b83b49e5015eb1c89fd25c","tid":562861,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"1.6都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d17cae61fad485ca6e85eb4939acc1b9f50bcd5","tid":562861,"uid":76757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921f806c8564247f589f27b5bee31cc92cfb303f","tid":562861,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"人地中一姐<br />\n但講到好似米六就夠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /